METHOD
    1 ssh-keygen -t rsa
    2 set up config file on  MacBook (.ssh directory)

      Host tomgdigo
            HostName 46.101.11.172
            User tomgdow
            Port 22

    3 ssh-copy-id -i id_rsa_pub tomgdigo 

    4 That is all!! 'ssh tomgdigo' now works perfectly

